-Mabuti ito.

543
00:38:16,210 --> 00:38:17,520
Maganda naman ang balkonahe, 'di ba?

544
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:17,960
Ang galing.

545
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:20,290
Dumaan ka nang mas madalas. Magmukhang parang nasa bahay ka lang.

546
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,100
Walang problema.

547
00:38:21,210 --> 00:38:21,690
Sige.

548
00:38:21,770 --> 00:38:22,960
Lumipat tayo sa ibang laro.

549
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,770
Laruin natin ito. Maglaro tayo ng baraha.

550
00:38:24,770 --> 00:38:26,040
Hayaan mong isipin ko...

551
